column2: "One stream has grown into many strands, this is divine providence."
"There is not much real value in any one of those conclusions."
"To us that holds no meaning. Yet we know that it may prove invaluable to you."
"Unusually this is something that I and We know, and you accept."
"Or is it that you accept without knowing the consequences?"
"From here on, new outcomes must be something that you find for yourself."
"In order for you to find that, that is why I and We are here."
